Introduction
Unknown subject 1, more commonly referred to as “French Fry,” was the founding member of the “Revolutionists.” Born during the era before IDs were a mandatory requirement he was born into an affluent family that made up the fledgling upper class. French Fry did not hold an occupation, but he was educated in the subject of Nuclear Physics. French Fry vehemently opposed the establishment of the current system.

As a survivor of the fracture he set about establishing the Revolutionists as a measure to oppose both WISDOM and the Traditionalists. He believed the main principles of society should be: the greater fluency between classes within the system, equal access to education, and the right to privacy for all citizens in the system. In the year 2100 AD French Fry attempted a revolution against the system, but ultimately failed in his attempted uprising. He continued to work with the Revolutionists until his death in the year 2160. The specifics behind his passing are unknown.

During life, he was often described as immensely intelligent and had a great passion towards education. Both WISDOM and the Traditionalists classify French Fry as a terrorist. It is recommended that anyone speaking of this man or associated with him be reported immediately to WISDOM and local authorities.

Appearance
Although there are no official records of French Fry, he is commonly described as having long blonde hair and glasses. He is said to have looked calm and wore unassuming clothing. He is known by the scar that crosses his left eyebrow as a souvenir from the apocalypse.

Personality
A lot can be assumed when you first see French Fry, but the biggest two things to know are that he's intuitive and confident. Of course he's also faithful, honorable and innovative, but they're less prominent and often intertwined with being obnoxious as well. His intuition though, this is what he's often admired for. There are many times when others count on this and his incisive nature whenever they need help. Nobody's perfect of course and French Fry has plenty of rainy days too. His difficult nature and arrogant nature cause plenty of grievances and beyond what people are willing to deal with. Fortunately his confidence assures this isn't the case very often.
